<div class="bg">
  <div class="bg-color">
    <div class="container content">
      <%= render partial: 'layouts/partials/flash' %>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="sun clearfix">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
             <h1>DeeBooster</h1>
             <h3>The world's most advanced sunbathing tool</h3>
          </div>
          <div id="left-block" class="col-sm-6 text-center">
            <img class="img-responsive" src="<%= asset_path 'tab.png' %>" alt="tab"/>
          </div>
          <div id="right-block" class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-8">
                <p class="alert-success"></p>
                <p class="alert-warning"></p>
                <h3>Join now and start producing vitamin D with your own body</h3>
                <form class="newsletter-signup" role="form">
                  <div class="input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-btn">
                      <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-sand btn-blue" %>
                    </span>
                    <span class="input-group-btn">
                      <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-sand" %>
                    </span>
                  </div><!-- /input-group -->
                </form>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="followus"></p>
            <ul class="social-icon">
              <li><a href=""><i class="fa fa-camera-retro"></i></a></li>
              <li><a href=""><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
              <li><a href=""><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a></li>
              <li><a href=""><i class="fa fa-youtube-square"></i></a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
    </div>
  </div>  
</div>
<div class="clearfix"></div>
<div class="content-section-b">
  <div class="container">
  <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-1 col-sm-push-6  col-sm-6">
          <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
          <div class="clearfix"></div>
          <h2 class="section-heading">Simple and Seamless<br>No complex forms</h2>
          <p class="lead">You don't need complex devices that are hard to use.</p>
          <p class="lead">You don't need to manually fill forms fields.</p>
          <p class="lead">DeeBoost detects seamlessly your current time <i class="fa fa-calendar"></i> and geographic location <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>in order to find the best time intervals for Vitamin D production.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-pull-6  col-sm-6">
        <img class="img-responsive" src="<%= asset_path 'dog.png' %>" alt=""/>
      </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="content-section-a">
  <div class="container">
  <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-6">
          <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
          <div class="clearfix"></div>
          <h2 class="section-heading">Deeboost is available<br>on any device</h2>
          <p class="lead">DeeBoost's web interface is responsive. That means it is optimized for all screen sizes <i class="fa fa-desktop"></i> including smartphones <i class="fa fa-mobile"></i> and tablets <i class="fa fa-tablet"></i> .</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-2 col-sm-6">
        <img class="img-responsive" src="<%= asset_path 'phones.png' %>" alt=""/>
      </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="content-section-b">
  <div class="container">
  <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-1 col-sm-push-6  col-sm-6">
          <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
          <div class="clearfix"></div>
          <h2 class="section-heading">Manage multiple locations<br></h2>
          <p class="lead">If you travel you can save different locations in DeeBoost.</p>
          <p class="lead">You can switch between saved locations with one simple click  <i class="fa fa-hand-pointer-o"></i> to view the data for a specific location.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-pull-6  col-sm-6">
        <img class="img-responsive" src="<%= asset_path 'ipad.png' %>" alt=""/>
      </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>


